<p>This tool allows you to import a form from the 
<a href="/form">Form builder</a> as a content item. When importing a form you 
define the form to use and also the size and padding for the content 
container.</p>

<p>The size and padding values will be defaulted based upon the size of the 
page container, the values will also be validated when the tool is being 
processed, you cannot add a content container which is larger than the page 
container.</p>

<p>In edit mode you will be able to define the styling for the content 
container.</p>